data.description: WELCOME HOME! This 3 bed 2.5 bath wonderful home backs up to open space and doesn't have another house to the right. Lots of mature trees give it a very private feeling. The main level has luxury vinyl flooring throughout. An open concept kitchen, dining room, living room is perfect for entertaining guests or just being able to be together. The kitchen has an island, pantry and lots of cabinets for plenty of storage. The upper level includes the primary bedroom that has its own fireplace, a 5 piece bathroom and a walk in closet. There are two other bedrooms, a full bath, the large loft and a laundry room. Close to the military bases and convenient to shopping, parks, etc. You won't want to miss this home!
